'''Boondheere''' waa Degmo Qadiimi ah oo ka tirsan Degmooyinka Gobolka [[Banaadir]]. Degmadan waxaa mara Wadooyinka kala ah: Waddada Jenaraal Daa'uud oo Boondheere ka marta dhinaca Degmada [[Wardhiigley|Wardhiigley.]] Waddada Jubadda Sare oo marta dhinaca Degmada [[Shibis]]. Waddada Ummada ama sida loo yaqaan  "Wadnaha" oo marta dhinaca Degmada [[Yaaqshiid]]. Waddada Jubadda Hoose oo marta dhinaca Degmada [[Shingaani]]. Waddada Nasiib Buundo oo Degmada Boondheere kala qeybisa iyo Waddada Shabeelle ee xuduudka u ah Degmooyinka Boondheere iyo [[Xamarweyne]].

